OL,3,CMajor incident declared as 'large-
OL,4,Cscale' wildfire forces locals to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FA major incident has been declared by
OL,8,Femergency services tackling a "large-
OL,9,Fscale" wildfire near Sychnant Pass on
OL,10,FConwy Mountain.
OL,12,FIt comes as some residents in the
OL,13,Fvillage of Capelulo, near Penmaenmawr
OL,14,Fin Conwy, had been advised to evacuate
OL,15,Ftheir homes for safety.
OL,17,FEmergency services have said that they
OL,18,Fare fighting the blaze amid
OL,19,F"challenging" conditions and that it
OL,20,Fcould continue "for some time."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
