OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784029691
OL,3,CMajor incident declared as 'large-
OL,4,Cscale' wildfire forces locals to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FResidents in the nearby communities of
OL,8,FDwygyfylchi and Penmaenmawr have been
OL,9,Fwarned to keep windows and doors
OL,10,Fclosed and to seek medical advice if
OL,11,Fthey experience breathing difficulties.
OL,13,FMembers of the public have been
OL,14,Fadvised to avoid travelling to the
OL,15,Faffected area and to follow evacuation
OL,16,Fadvice or safety instructions issued
OL,17,Fby the emergency services.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
