OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784029691
OL,3,CMajor incident declared as 'large-
OL,4,Cscale' wildfire forces locals to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FIn a statement on Sunday afternoon,
OL,8,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,9,FDelivery Manager Jami Jennings said:
OL,10,F"Firefighters remain on scene working
OL,11,Fin challenging conditions to contain
OL,12,Fthe fire and protect surrounding
OL,13,Fcommunities, property, infrastructure
OL,14,Fand the environment...
OL,16,F"The incident involves a co-ordinated
OL,17,Fresponse from multiple fire
OL,18,Fappliances, specialist wildfire
OL,19,Fresources and partner agencies.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
