FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784029691
OL,3,CMajor incident declared as 'large-
OL,4,Cscale' wildfire forces locals to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,F"Due to the size and complexity of the
OL,8,Fincident, operations are expected to
OL,9,Fcontinue for some time....
OL,11,F"This response is being managed in
OL,12,Fclose collaboration with our partners,
OL,13,Fincluding the police, ambulance
OL,14,Fservice, local authority, landowners
OL,15,Fand environmental agencies.
OL,17,F"We will continue to assess the
OL,18,Fsituation and deploy resources where
OL,19,Fthey are needed most.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
