PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784029691
OL,3,CMajor incident declared as 'large-
OL,4,Cscale' wildfire forces locals to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,F"North Wales Police are co-ordinating
OL,8,Fthe evacuation strategy for residents
OL,9,Fwho should present themselves at the
OL,10,Fagreed rest centre.
OL,12,F"We appreciate the patience and co-
OL,13,Foperation of the community and would
OL,14,Falso like to thank our firefighters,
OL,15,Fcontrol staff, partner agencies and
OL,16,Fvolunteers whose professionalism and
OL,17,Fcommitment are helping to bring this
OL,18,Fincident under control."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
